channel.title: What do you dislike about RS07?
channel.description: Well haven't seen one of these, so what do you dislike about rs07? I'll be getting it soon and was curious if theres anything I should watch for.

item.title: What do you dislike about RS07?
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

[quote=“Muroth, post:29, topic:495671”][quote author=Tutorial link=topic=613903.msg4241053#msg4241053 date=1361833479]

People trading EOC gold for 07. Cheating IMO.

Yeh, but it isn’t having a negative effect on the game itself. The gold still has to be produced from an original source.
[/quote]

It will eventually when more and more bots come along[/quote]
Obviously it will, but he wasn’t referring to the source of the gold, but rather the exchange between gold, even though the gold stays on the server it was on (duh).
